<!-- WHY ASENSO -->
<section id="why">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="section-tag">Why Asenso</div>
        <h2>Boutique service.<br>Big-firm credentials.</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">The large labs have the lab footprint. What they can't give you is a principal who answers the phone, an inspector who knows your project, and a firm that moves at your pace.</p>
        <div class="why-features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-num">01</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>The same inspector, start to finish</h4>
              <p>No rotating staff, no hand-off gaps. The inspector at your pre-con meeting is on-site every phase — and remembers what was agreed at the last one.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-num">02</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Reports that hold up in front of agencies</h4>
              <p>Field reports issued same day, formatted for the AHJ, SEOR, and owner. Written to satisfy the building department — not just to check a box.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-num">03</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>You can reach us when it matters</h4>
              <p>Mid-pour and need an answer fast? Call us directly. No call center, no dispatch queue — you get the inspector or a principal, immediately.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-num">04</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Family-built, credential-proven</h4>
              <p>Asenso is family-owned and family-staffed. Every cert on our team is real, current, and earned — not borrowed from a subcontractor we'll dispatch without telling you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
