<!-- PROCESS -->
<section id="process">
  <div class="pattern-bg">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 900 500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"><defs><pattern id="dot" x="0" y="0" width="30" height="30" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="15" cy="15" r="1" fill="#EAE2D6" opacity=".055"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#dot)"/></svg>
  </div>
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">How We Work</div>
    <h2>SSI review to permit closeout.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Structured around your project schedule — not a lab's dispatch queue.</p>
    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="process-step"><div class="step-num">01</div><div class="step-div"></div><h4>SSI &amp; Drawing Review</h4><p>We review the Statement of Special Inspections, structural drawings, and specs before the first pour. No surprises in the field.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><div class="step-num">02</div><div class="step-div"></div><h4>Pre-Construction Meeting</h4><p>We align with the GC, SEOR, and AHJ on inspection scope, hold points, phasing, and reporting expectations before work begins.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><div class="step-num">03</div><div class="step-div"></div><h4>Field Inspections</h4><p>On-site per your SSI — continuous or periodic. Same-day digital field reports. Same inspector every visit.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><div class="step-num">04</div><div class="step-div"></div><h4>Closeout Package</h4><p>Final summary report, all field logs, NCR resolution, and observation letters — compiled and ready for AHJ submittal.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

